  <teaser>Hardt was founded by the winners of Elon Musk’s hyperloop competition and has grown towards 40 people. The dream is realizing the Europan Hyperloop Network. A 10,000 kilometre hyperloop network crossing national borders: we are realizing a world where distance doesn´t...</teaser>
  <objective>Hardt was founded by the winners of Elon Musk’s hyperloop competition and has grown towards 40 people. The dream is realizing the Europan Hyperloop Network. A 10,000 kilometre hyperloop network crossing national borders: we are realizing a world where distance doesn´t matter, where opportunities are open to everyone. If Europe wants to go climate neutral in 2050, now is the time to invest in future-proof transportation. In the coming decades, the passenger and freight demand will triple. To handle these enormous traffic flows, infrastructure investments of up to 70 trillion Euros are needed. Hardt introduces the hyperloop:
-	A reliable and fast mode of transportation
-	The cleanest alternative for transportation
-	The safest and most convenient way of transportation
We are Hardt Hyperloop. We envision a world, where you can live, work, and be, wherever you want, whenever you want. Join us in building future-proof transportation for a sustainable and hyper-connected Europe.</objective>
  <title>Hyperloop, for smarter, faster, greener and better transportation starting with freight</title>
